test_cases.objective: Verify that user can sign in using a valid email and password
test_steps: Navigate to the login page
Enter valid email and password in the respective fields and click on 'Continue'
Expect the application to authenticate the user successfully and redirect to the dashboard page
Check if the user is successfully logged in
Verify that all functionalities are working as expected
Verify if the dev mode label is displayed or not
expected_results: User should be able to login with valid credentials
Application should redirect to the dashboard page after successful login
All functionalities should work as expected
Dev mode label should be displayed or not

test_cases.objective: Verify that user cannot sign in with an invalid email and password
test_steps: Navigate to the login page
Enter invalid email and password in the respective fields and click on 'Continue'
Expect the application to show an error message indicating invalid credentials
Verify that all functionalities are working as expected
Check if the dev mode label is displayed or not
expected_results: User should not be able to login with invalid credentials
Application should display an error message indicating invalid credentials
All functionalities should work as expected
Dev mode label should be displayed or not
